home-page.need_comfortable_ride: Need a comfortable ride? Want a ride instantly or schedule for later? Wow Taxi gets you a ride from where you need up to you want to go, ensuring a safe and affordable ride.
home-page.book_with_eber: There will be no hidden charges. A driver will pick you up on time and drop you at the entered destination following the fastest routes on the map.
home-page.login_to_book_taxi: Login Now to Book a Taxi Online
home-page.looking_for_worldclass_taxi: Looking for a Worldclass Online Taxi Booking Experience?
home-page.get_started_with_eber_taxi: Get started with our Wow taxi application, as it will help you find the most dependable taxi services anytime and anywhere. From finding a fixed price to scheduling the ride to making payment from multiple options, it's all possible with us.
home-page.the_best_way_to_travel: The best way to travel to your destination with easy online booking options
home-page.do_you_need_taxi_at_your_doorsteps: Do You Need a Taxi at Your Doorsteps?
home-page.choose_eber_fixed_prices: Choose Wow and Book Your Taxi at Fixed Prices
home-page.options_for_where_you_going: We’ve got options to get you where you’re going. Your ride will be comfortable and affordable with our variety of taxis viable for ride-hailing and ride-sharing.
home-page.download_eber_for_booking: Download the Wow app for attractive deals and ease of online booking.
home-page.about_rentals: With Wow’s Rental services, you get a taxi at your disposal. You can rent a taxi for a short period of time in the day. Whether you want to attend a meeting, a trip to the outskirts of the city, or just want to visit popular places within the town, our taxi rental facility has covered all. All you need to do is enter the necessary details such as contact information, how many hours you need a taxi, pay with a convenient method,and you are done.
home-page.about_taxi_hailing1: Far from the city location? Don’t worry. Book a taxi with Wow wherever you are and know in advance what the exact price of your ride will be. Enter contact details along with pick up-drop addresses and get the taxi in no time at your preferred location.
home-page.about_taxi_hailing2: Avoid any nasty surprises with Wow. We will show you accurate prices before you choose your ride. Our prices are calculated on the basis of kilometers and are comparatively lower than others.What’s more? Book or schedule a ride, share and rate your ride at your fingertips 24/7
home-page.about_ride_share1: Now share a ride with your friends or colleagues. Simply enter the details with whom you are about to share the ride. Wow helps commuters to start sharing the ride instead of traveling alone.
home-page.about_ride_share2: Connect, match the routes, coordinate and share total cost in a seamless manner within the app. Wow automates the end-to-end process of car sharing and makes the entire journey comfortable and affordable for the passengers.
home-page.about_split_payment1: Split the fare with other passengers and enjoy the ride together. Yes, you can split the fare with co-passengers that have an account on the platform. Split the taxi bill between all the passengers and pay only your fare from your respective account.
home-page.about_split_payment2: Wow allows the users to split the total bill within the app. This feature is highly suitable for those who share the same route daily. It makes the ride affordable and convenient by splitting the bill with other passengers equally.
home-page.about_driver_going_to_home1: Whenever the driver is about to finish his working hours, he can add the status in the app. The rides that start from the nearby location and have a destination on his route to home or nearby will be assigned to the driver. In this ride, the driver can accept or reject the ride.
home-page.about_driver_going_to_home2: This way driver gets to earn from one more ride and earn a little extra. Moreover, this will save the driver time to conduct an extra ride. All of this makes ride-hailing more convenient and efficient for riders and drivers.
home-page.about_multiple_stop1: Riders, while booking the ride, can add multiple stops during the ride. For all these stops, they will have to pay extra fees depending on the stops and the time it holds at each location.
home-page.about_multiple_stop2: Drivers will stop the ride at each location and will start the timer to record the duration of the stop. It makes the ride convenient for the riders,as they can fulfill several purposes in a single ride.
